Source: uv
Section: misc
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/astral-sh/uv

Package: uv
Architecture: amd64
Description: An extremely fast Python package and project manager, written in Rust.
 uv is a fast Python package installer and resolver, designed as a
 drop-in replacement for pip, pip-tools, and virtualenv. It also
 serves as a Python project manager similar to rye or poetry.
